title: The H.P. Lovecraft Ebook Library (2014 Update) -emidius-
description:
The H.P. Lovecraft Ebook Library (2014 Update) -emidius-

I have tried to include Epub, Mobi, and PDF versions. You may see more than one copy of a work. This is not a mistake, but because different editors were either light or heavy handed while editing his works. Much depending on the era. So I decided to decided to include absolutley everything I could find!
